{"tid":1885700,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"孫興敏手臂骨折勢唞兩個月","createTime":"2020-02-18T12:43:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T14:40:46.000Z","uid":16659,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"335eb6819d0777a6676ce0f27bd3fb3f5b808d01","tid":1885700,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T12:43:21.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】熱刺周二宣佈，前鋒孫興敏手臂骨折，盛傳將要休息8星期。<br />\n<br />\n孫興敏（Son Heung-min）在上場英超攻入絕殺球，帶領熱刺以3:2險勝阿士東維拉，但賽後證實手臂骨折，將會在本周進行手術，預計休息數星期。<br />\n<br />\n熱刺未有表明這名韓國國腳需要休息多少個星期，但網媒《The Athletic》指，孫興敏將要休息8個星期；他在周日之戰，開局跟對方守將干沙相撞時受創，經治理後捱足全場。<br />\n<br />\n熱刺早已有射手哈利簡尼因為腿筋傷患，最快要到4月才復出，如今再有在對上5場場場有波入的孫興敏受傷，對於在英超爭前4打擊甚大。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"88d9865c122f7166ff164982cd9865ccdd11ed76","tid":1885700,"uid":17311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T12:48:28.000Z","msg":"??佢唔係好早傷? 仲以為冇事"},{"pid":"02f285de87a0651101b447793141fb17f7bb98fa","tid":1885700,"uid":111460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T12:49:01.000Z","msg":"打丁太用力？"},{"pid":"f4c2db39af15b26240b854c481e6bcab7d829d70","tid":1885700,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T12:49:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/b3c5eb7cb5cee54d5598492640e0f6d8/e9d7dc43deea9ed6-74/s640x960/142f41e0dc53f0dfdbb5cacc6ccccc4ec9f54f66.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2Fb3c5eb7cb5cee54d5598492640e0f6d8%2Fe9d7dc43deea9ed6-74%2Fs640x960%2F142f41e0dc53f0dfdbb5cacc6ccccc4ec9f54f66.jpg&h=4a81a107&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a80db6259f7397acbfd5d206d9d3d073a07dfd15","tid":1885700,"uid":222907,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T12:49:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3bQDQxM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3bQDQxM.gif&h=eb0e1c63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n波品韓國天王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 